post_title: How can I safely cook chicken drumsticks in the microwave oven?

======================================================

(You): How can I safely cook chicken drumsticks in the microwave oven?

(Asbah): They might dry out a bit but continue to heat them until fully cooked, it may take a while. A marinade might do them well as well as constant basting.

(You): ok, but how long should I cook them to make sure its safe.. HIGH at how many minutes

(Asbah): It really depends on your microwave time.  I would do 5 minute intervals on high, turning the legs every few minutes (stop every 3 min or so), to make sure all of the meat on the bone gets cooked evenly.

